flowchart LR
  User[User / Reviewer] --> Swagger[Swagger UI]
  Swagger --> API[FastAPI Backend]
  API --> Routes[Routes: Data ML Agents Analytics]
  Routes --> ML[RandomForestClassifier for symptom triage]
  Routes --> DB[(MongoDB / Cosmos DB)]
  Routes --> RAG[RAG Pipeline]
  RAG --> KB[(Knowledge Base + Embeddings)]
  RAG --> LLM[Azure OpenAI or Fallback]
  Routes --> MCP[MCP-style Orchestrator]
  ML --> Artifacts[(Joblib Model + Metrics)]
  API --> PowerBI[Power BI CSV Export]
  API --> Azure[Azure App Service]
